Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.cache

Interface IntArray

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, MemoryStatsVisitor.Visitable, NumberArray<IntArray>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicIntArray, HeapIntArray, OffHeapIntArray, PageCacheIntArray
    public interface IntArray
extends NumberArray<IntArray>
    Abstraction of a int[] so that different implementations can be plugged in, for example off-heap, dynamically growing, or other implementations.
    See Also:

      • swap

        default void swap​(long fromIndex,
                  long toIndex)
        Description copied from interface: NumberArray
        Swaps items from fromIndex to toIndex, such that fromIndex and toIndex, fromIndex+1 and toIndex a.s.o swaps places. The number of items swapped is equal to the length of the default value of the array.
        Specified by:
        swap in interface NumberArray<IntArray>
        Parameters:
        fromIndex - where to start swapping from.
        toIndex - where to start swapping to.
